body:
I havent been on tumblr for a about a week due to toxicity, but I have to get on for a moment just to state that

Dan and Phil are the most lovely people I’ve ever seen and they are gifts from Heaven and not a single thing they’ve done I don’t think could truly make them look bad and I love them with Every. Ounce. Of. My. Soul.

Thank you, goodnight, I’ll see you all in about another week.
